// Syncthing global ignore patterns
// Managed by NixOS flake (modules/common/stignore).
// Do NOT edit the deployed copy on disk — change this file and redeploy.
// Syntax: https://docs.syncthing.net/users/ignoring.html

// ----- Git internals (constant pack/index/ref churn + corruption risk) -----
**/.git

// ----- Python -----
**/.venv
**/venv
**/.env
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.tox
**/*.egg-info
**/.ipynb_checkpoints

// ----- Node / JS / TS -----
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.nuxt
**/.turbo
**/.parcel-cache
**/.svelte-kit
**/.astro
**/dist
**/build
**/out
**/.yarn/cache
**/.yarn/install-state.gz
**/.pnpm-store

// ----- Rust / Java / Scala / Go -----
**/target
**/.gradle
**/.mvn
**/*.class
**/vendor

// ----- Terraform / OpenTofu / Pulumi -----
**/.terraform
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.backup
**/.tofu
**/.pulumi

// ----- Nix / direnv -----
